        <Parent_String>Pre-Columbian Andean styles and periods [300017257], Pre-Columbian South American styles and periods [300017250], Pre-Columbian (American) [300016619], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
